  69:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_GetPulseLow() function to get the minimum guaranteed
  70:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        duration of the pwr_on low pulse in Standby mode.
  71:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  72:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableTCMFLXRetention() and HAL_PWREx_DisableTCMFLXRetention()
  73:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        functions to enable and disable the I-TCM FLEXMEM retention in Standby mode.
  74:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  75:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableSMPSPWM() and HAL_PWREx_DisableSMPSPWM() functions to
  76:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        enable and disable the SMPS low-power mode in Stop SVOS range 3.
