 254:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         This parameter can be one of the following values :
 255:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *            @arg @ref PWR_SMPS_SUPPLY            : VCORE power domains are supplied
