 466:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****     [..]
 467:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       By default the content of BKPSRAM memories aren't retained in Standby mode.
 468:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       By setting the BKPRBSEN bit in the PWR_BDCR2 register using the
 469:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       HAL_PWREx_EnableBkupRAMRetention() function, the content of these memories
 470:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       are retained even in Standby mode.
